Package com.example.drinks.DrinksOrderData

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OrderDAO
    OrderDAO is an interface that is used by the CustomerDB class This is a DAO that is used to get the data from the database as well as insert new entries
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddDrinkOrderViewer
    A class used to add a new Drink order
    CustomerOrdersAdapter
    A class which is used to Display the customers orders
    DrinkOrder
    DrinkOrder Class This class is an entity in the OrderDB This class generates a Primary key and stores the customersID Price of a drink and the name of the drink
    DrinkOrderAdapter
    A class which Displays all the orders a customer has ordered
    OrderDB
    An abstract class which stores the framework of the Database This Database stores the DrinkOrder Class as its entities
